# ✅ Step 4: Run & Test (Very Important)

### ✅ First Load (Online)

1.  Start the app
2.  Data loads from API
3.  Service Worker **caches `/api/users`**

✅ Cache filled

***

### ✅ Open a New Tab

1.  Open the same app URL in a **new tab**
2.  Service Worker already exists
3.  API response is served **from cache**

✅ Same data  
✅ Faster load  
✅ No extra API call

***

### ✅ Go Offline

1.  Open DevTools → Network → **Offline**
2.  Refresh the page
3.  Data still appears

✅ This is **true offline support**

***

